ldren":[{"type":"text","value":"既使已通報清潔隊，仍可裁處 6,000 元 罰款。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-07.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-07.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園內禁止騎機車/自行車"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長樂公園旁有 Ubike 站點, 在長樂公園內常有騎車者按鈴驅趕小孩及年長者！ 原則上公園內是不能騎車的。 而騎車者喧賓奪主 按鈴驅趕行人更為惡劣。 既使在人車共用步道, 也須緩慢通過"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要按鈴"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 幼兒及年長者會被驚嚇到。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有些人認為 按鈴是提醒注意。 那麼在車道上汽車接近自行車/機車也都按喇叭提醒慢車注意， 是否合適呢？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-11.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-11.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝龜山區公所的定期除草及清理工作。 公園中原有的空中電纜近期已被清除了！ 電纜下方的無障礙步道與公園間的障礙也改善完成。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在下龜山的區公所對 A7 公園的維護也更用心了, 感謝！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-10.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-10.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"公園的維護","depth":2,"text":"公園的維護","children":[{"id":"公園禁止的項目宣導","depth":3,"text":"公園禁止的項目宣導"},{"id":"文德公園的改善重點項目","depth":3,"text":"文德公園的改善重點項目"},{"id":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業","depth":3,"text":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:resident:r037.md","_source":"content","_file":"resident/r037.md","_extension":"md"}